Welcome to Sultana's Kitchen

A Culinary Adventure For All The Senses.

As Sultana began to expand her repertoire in the kitchen and consider starting a home business, she realised that there was a gap in the market for the kind of food she cooked at home - traditional Indian cuisine that was free from artificial food flavouring and colours, “cheap substitute” ingredients (eg. adding extra fat from meat instead of using ghee) and that relied on old-fashioned.

Sultana’s Kitchen thus came to life — homemade, heritage Indian cuisine that combines old-fashioned cooking techniques and made-from-scratch recipes to bring you food that is rich in flavour, history and culture.

read more about us

Our Menu

You can now experience a bit of Sultana’s hospitality in your own home, with her made-to-order Heritage Biryani, Speciality Curries and Middle Eastern Mandi menus.

WHY CHOOSE US

Your Perfect
Choice To Enjoy Heritage Indian cuisine

She sources her ingredients from only the best - whether it’s black pepper directly from growers in Kerala,
saffron from Kashmir or using only the finest quality meat,
there is simply NO cutting corners when it comes to quality, flavour and authenticity.
